HEADWORD: Refracture
<hw>Re*frac"ture</hw> <pr>(r?*fr?k"t?r;135)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Surg.)</fld> <def>A second breaking (as of a badly set bone) by
the surgeon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Refracture</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Refracture
<hw>Re*frac"ture</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <fld>(Surg.)</fld> <def>To break
again, as a bone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Refragable</ent>⟦br⟧
